These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, lemonade, mirinda, water
City: edinburgh, marseilles, colone, london
1. the person traveling to edinburgh is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to colone##5
2. the person drinking lemonade is not the person traveling to edinburgh##6
3. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the right of the person traveling to london##1
4. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person traveling to colone##1
5. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
6. the person traveling to edinburgh is not the person drinking mirinda##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |    2     |    3     |    4    |
| Beverage   | lemonade   | water    | juice    | mirinda |
| Sport      | london | edinburgh | colone | marseilles |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, milk, mirinda, sprite
There are 4 different favourite colors: azure, lavender, pink, grey
1. the person who likes azure is on the far right##1
2. the person drinking milk is somewhere to the left of the person drinking mirinda##5
3. the person who likes grey is somewhere to the left of the person drinking sprite##5
4. the person drinking milk is not the person who likes lavender##6
5. the person who likes grey is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
6. the person who likes azure is on the right of the person who likes pink##1
7. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
8. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere to the left of the person drinking iced-tea##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Beverage   | milk  | mirinda    | iced-tea | sprite    |
| Food       | grey | lavender | pink  | azure |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-3::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, march, february, january
The people have 4 different jobs:  coach, doctor, electrician, police-officer
1. the person who's birthday is in january is not the coach##6
2. the doctor is not the person who's birthday is in february##6
3. the electrician is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in march##3
4. the doctor is the person who's birthday is in november##1
5. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the doctor##1
6. the person who's birthday is in november is in an odd position##4
7. the coach is on the far left or far right##3
8. the electrician is somewhere to the left of the police-officer##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |       2        |   3    |   4    |
| Beverage   | january       | march  | november  | february |
| Job        | electrician | police-officer | doctor | coach  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-4::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: aquamarine, azure, brown, orange
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, subway, train, trike
1. the person who likes brown is on the left of the person who likes orange##1
2. the person who likes azure is somewhere to the left of the person driving the quad-bike##5
3. the person driving the trike is not the person who likes azure##6
4. the person driving the trike is somewhere to the right of the person driving the quad-bike##5
5. the person driving the train is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
6. the person who likes orange is somewhere to the left of the person driving the trike##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |     3     |    4     |
| Pet         | azure | brown | orange     | aquamarine |
| Transport   | subway     | train    | quad-bike | trike    |

