.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-6::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, mystery, spy, thriller
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: metal, salsa, d&b, indie
1. the fan metal is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
2. the person watching thriller movies is not the fan salsa##6
3. the fan metal is on the far right##1
4. the fan salsa is somewhere to the right of the fan indie##5
5. the person watching spy movies is the person watching spy movies##1
6. the person watching spy movies is somewhere to the left of the fan metal##5
7. the person watching spy movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching disaster movies##5
8. the person watching mystery movies is somewhere to the left of the fan indie##5
9. the person watching mystery movies is somewhere to the left of the fan indie##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |     3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | spy    | disaster  | thriller   |
| Nationality   | d&b  | indie | salsa | metal |

