.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-10::.
4 different pets are kept: ferret, fish, hedgehog, rabbit
There are 4 different nationalities: french, australian, italian, colombian
1. the french is not the owner of the ferret##6
2. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
3. the colombian is the colombian##1
4. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the colombian##1
5. the owner of the hedgehog is not the colombian##6
6. the australian is not the owner of the fish##6
7. the colombian is in an even position##4
8. the owner of the hedgehog is the french##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |       2       |    3    |    4     |
| Pet     | hedgehog | ferret        | rabbit  | fish     |
| Sport   | french     | colombian | australian | italian |

