.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-11::.
4 different pets are kept: fish, rabbit, chinchilla, pony
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, electronic, indie, pop
1. the owner of the fish is on the left or right of the owner of the pony##3
2. the fan electronic is somewhere to the left of the owner of the fish##5
3. the fan indie is not the owner of the chinchilla##6
4. the owner of the rabbit is between the fan pop and the owner of the chinchilla##2
5. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
6. the fan electronic is between the fan disco and the owner of the fish##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |   3   |     4     |
| Hobby         | chinchilla | rabbit    | fish | pony |
| Music-Genre   | disco         | electronic | pop   | indie     |

