.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-12::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: zombie, action, superhero, documentary
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, bus, snowmobile, trike
1. the person watching superhero movies is somewhere to the right of the person driving the snowmobile##5
2. the person watching documentary movies is not the person driving the bike##6
3. the person driving the bus is the person watching documentary movies##1
4. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
5. the person driving the snowmobile is not the person watching documentary movies##6
6. the person watching action movies is not the person driving the bike##6
7. the person watching superhero movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching action movies##5
8. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |     3     |   4    |
| Food        | zombie  | superhero | action | documentary |
| Transport   | snowmobile | bike     | trike     | bus    |

