.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-15::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: black, amber, light-blue, grey
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, climbing, cricket, water-polo
1. the person who's sport is baseball is in an odd position##4
2. the person who likes black is on the left or right of the person who likes light-blue##3
3. the person who's sport is climbing is not the person who likes black##6
4. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
5. the person who's sport is cricket is between the person who likes amber and the person who's sport is climbing##2
6. the person who likes amber is not the person who's sport is baseball##6
7. the person who likes grey is on the right of the person who likes light-blue##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2     |     3     |     4      |
| Job     | black  | light-blue | grey | amber |
| Sport   | baseball | climbing | cricket   | water-polo |

