3. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
4. the fisherman is on the left or right of the bartender##3
5. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the far right##1
6. the bartender is not the person who's sport is water-polo##6

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Sport       | lacrosse | basketball | water-polo | volleyball |
| Transport   | firefighter   | dressmaker       | fisherman    | bartender     |

