.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-20::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, iced-tea, mirinda, water
House: gothic-revival, modern, tower, cape-cod
1. the cape-cod house is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3
2. the person drinking water is on the left or right of the modern house##3
3. the gothic-revival house is on the right of the tower house##1
4. the gothic-revival house is not the person drinking almond-milk##6
5. the person drinking water is somewhere to the right of the modern house##5
6. the modern house is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |    2     |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage    | almond-milk | iced-tea | water      | mirinda   |
| Transport   | cape-cod  | modern   | tower | gothic-revival |

 